  "title": "Client server Model",
  "slug": "client-server-model",
  "updated": "2026-06-11T07:21:57.860+05:30",
  "author": "Priya",
  "labels": [
    "Technical interview questions"
  ],
  "content": "<div class=\"full-card\">\n  <p>Client server model is a request/response service model in which 2 machines are involved for to and fro data movements.A request is made by client and sent through browser.It is processed and response is sent by server.Here server can be a mail server ,a database server or a cloud based web provider.And the response sent by the server can be a html response,an xml or a json.<br>\n    Some examples may be like - accessing gmail,online banking sites,web browsing.<br>\n    It's a bi-direactional request -response cycle in which client machine sends a request to the server and awaits response.It architecture is<br>  </p>\n    <ul style=\"display:block; list-style:disc; margin-left:20px;color:black;\">\n      <li><b>1-tier -</b> Everything on 1 machine.</li>\n      <li><b>2-tier - </b>A database server.Client accessing MYSQL database</li>\n   <li><b>3-tier -</b>Client ? App Server ? Database\nThis is the pattern behind most modern web/mobile systems.</li>\n      <li><b>N-tier -</b>Additional layers like API Gateway, Caching layer, Load Balancer, etc.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n</div><br>\n<div class=\"title-row\">\n\n<h2>Communication in a Client server architecture</h2>\n<!--\n<a href='https://rzp.io/rzp/PYRfP7l' id='pdfBtn' target='_blank'>\n  <b>Download PDF &#8377;10</b>\n</a>\n  <div\nid=\"pdf-download-container\" data-product=\"Java\"\ndata-pdf=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RDUbojETTY0P06maWHdmm7-6gMkmS_Bg/view?usp=sharing\">\n</div>  -->\n<button onclick=\"\nlocalStorage.setItem('pdf_product','client');\nwindow.location.href='https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RDUbojETTY0P06maWHdmm7-6gMkmS_Bg/view?usp=sharing';\n\" id='pdfBtn'>\n <b>Download PDF</b>\n</button>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n\n.full-card{\nwidth:100%;\nmax-width:100%;\nmargin:20px auto;\npadding:35px;\nbackground:#ffffff;\nborder-radius:18px;\nbox-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);\nfont-family:Arial,sans-serif;\nline-height:1.8;\nbox-sizing:border-box;\n}\n\n.full-card h1{\nfont-size:34px;\ncolor:#222;\nmargin-bottom:15px;\nline-height:1.3;\n}\n\n.full-card h2{\nfont-size:28px;\ncolor:#333;\nmargin-top:35px;\nmargin-bottom:15px;\n}\n\n.full-card p{\nfont-size:18px;\ncolor:#444;\nmargin-bottom:18px;\n}\n\n.full-card img{\nwidth:100%;\nborder-radius:12px;\nmargin:20px 0;\ndisplay:block;\n}\n\n.full-card ul{\npadding-left:22px;\n}\n\n.full-card li{\nmargin-bottom:10px;\nfont-size:18px;\n}\n\n.title-row{\ndisplay:flex !important;\nalign-items:center;\ngap:15px;\nflex-wrap:nowrap !important;\n}\n\n.title-row h2{\nmargin:0 !important;\nwidth:auto !important;\nflex:1;\n}\n\n/* BUTTON */\n\n#pdfBtn{\nposition:relative;\noverflow:hidden;\ndisplay:inline-block !important;\nbackground:linear-gradient(45deg,#00ff00,#00cc66);\ncolor:#fff;\npadding:12px 20px;\nborder-radius:14px;\nfont-weight:700;\ntext-decoration:none;\nfont-size:20px;\nwhite-space:nowrap;\nflex-shrink:0;\n\nbox-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(0,255,0,.45);\n\nanimation:pulse 2s infinite;\ntransition:.35s ease;\n}\n\n/* Hover motion */\n\n#pdfBtn:hover{\ntransform:translateY(-4px) scale(1.05);\nbox-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(0,255,0,.65);\n}\n\n/* Moving shiny wave */\n\n#pdfBtn::before{\ncontent:\"\";\nposition:absolute;\ntop:0;\nleft:-120%;\nwidth:60%;\nheight:100%;\n\nbackground:rgba(255,255,255,.45);\n\ntransform:skewX(-30deg);\n\nanimation:shine 2.5s infinite;\n}\n\n/* Ripple circle */\n\n#pdfBtn::after{\ncontent:\"\";\nposition:absolute;\nleft:50%;\ntop:50%;\n\nwidth:12px;\nheight:12px;\n\nbackground:rgba(255,255,255,.55);\n\nborder-radius:50%;\n\ntransform:translate(-50%,-50%);\nanimation:ripple 1.8s infinite;\n}\n\n/* Pulse */\n\n@keyframes pulse{\n0%{\ntransform:scale(1);\n}\n50%{\ntransform:scale(1.06);\n}\n100%{\ntransform:scale(1);\n}\n}\n\n/* Shine animation */\n\n@keyframes shine{\n0%{\nleft:-120%;\n}\n100%{\nleft:160%;\n}\n}\n\n/* Ripple animation */\n\n@keyframes ripple{\n0%{\nopacity:.8;\ntransform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0);\n}\n100%{\nopacity:0;\ntransform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(12);\n}\n}\n\n</style><br><hr><br>\n\n<div id=\"image-grid\"></div>\n\n\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\"\nhref=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lightbox2/2.11.4/css/lightbox.min.css\">\n\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lightbox2/2.11.4/js/lightbox.min.js\"></script>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tesseract.js@5/dist/tesseract.min.js\"></script>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"source-images\" style=\"display:none;\">\n\n  \n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiL6U7EFQpBe-VfvMZZWw3CSMYwoz7-B-XB101QMG8ugCetVYDsA5zX7hkcl4XldFhdoIWBAwORKPHKFLJ04lqj3e7KwMLyD-JJCTDEJyBldtYo2qVGwo-L1PYIq8rsc4Yr5zmUzD7vpUBaEj36dt2a94EBZnDF0d0P6EY2jwuqWou_2S_P3_QSii2mkqM/s1280/IMG-20210723-WA0003.jpg\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1em 0; text-align: center; \"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiL6U7EFQpBe-VfvMZZWw3CSMYwoz7-B-XB101QMG8ugCetVYDsA5zX7hkcl4XldFhdoIWBAwORKPHKFLJ04lqj3e7KwMLyD-JJCTDEJyBldtYo2qVGwo-L1PYIq8rsc4Yr5zmUzD7vpUBaEj36dt2a94EBZnDF0d0P6EY2jwuqWou_2S_P3_QSii2mkqM/s320/IMG-20210723-WA0003.jpg\"/></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj8_-A7lXXhbKDC8fN6wwBIgzL8uM4v0Y0cTdmLUoeRCImf7_mh-QWb44K3741_dRGx_x_oLG6zjX6HJiTgaAtcgrbtZ1bA7nMJQ3qWb0YjDMr3rwVRqda2-mJhNHgZvjFsWdrlXJX_UeknjqsBnfNVDLAou9Gdm9X6cNzVn-xkCl_9lBH-P1TTGWufDdk/s1280/IMG-20210723-WA0004.jpg\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1em 0; text-align: center; \"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"320\" data-original-height=\"1280\" data-original-width=\"606\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj8_-A7lXXhbKDC8fN6wwBIgzL8uM4v0Y0cTdmLUoeRCImf7_mh-QWb44K3741_dRGx_x_oLG6zjX6HJiTgaAtcgrbtZ1bA7nMJQ3qWb0YjDMr3rwVRqda2-mJhNHgZvjFsWdrlXJX_UeknjqsBnfNVDLAou9Gdm9X6cNzVn